## 2) Art Asset Restrictions

### Important: art assets are non-commercial

All art assets in this repository (including but not limited to character sprites,
scene backgrounds, posters, furniture, plant sets, coffee machine assets, server
room assets, animations, and bundled packs) are non-commercial only.

These assets are provided for learning, demonstration, and experimentation.
You may not use these art assets for any commercial purpose.

If you plan a commercial use case, you must replace all art assets with your
own original work.

